A goal is an objective or target that an individual or organization aims to achieve. It is a desired outcome or result that guides and motivates actions and decisions. Goals provide focus, direction, and purpose by defining what needs to be accomplished within a specific timeframe. They can be short-term or long-term and can be related to various aspects of life, such as personal development, career advancement, health and fitness, financial stability, or business growth. Setting clear and measurable goals is important to track progress and stay motivated in the pursuit of success.
